verses.text: Praise ye the \+w LORD strong="H3050"\+w**. Praise, O ye servants of the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**, praise the name of the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**.+ 113.1 Praise ye…: Heb. Hallelujah*
Blessed be the name of the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w** from this time forth and for evermore.
From the rising of the sun unto the going down of the same the \+w LORD’s strong="H3068"\+w** name is* to be praised.
The \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w** is* high above all nations, and* his glory above the heavens.
Who is* like unto the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w** our God, who dwelleth on high,+ 113.5 dwelleth…: Heb. exalteth himself to dwell*
Who humbleth himself* to behold the things that are* in heaven, and in the earth!
He raiseth up the poor out of the dust, and* lifteth the needy out of the dunghill;
That he may set him* with princes, even* with the princes of his people.
He maketh the barren woman to keep house, and to be* a joyful mother of children. Praise ye the \+w LORD strong="H3050"\+w**.+ 113.9 to keep…: Heb. to dwell in an house*
